values:
LJ! There you are! o_O

So random post because people in chat were talking about LJ which made me think of my LJ... So i logged in (and amazingly got my password right on my first try)... And after going through some super old posts (some filled with old Lio drama, which made me cringe), I thought, HAY I SHOULD POST ON HERE. So here I am.

News point 1 of the day:
I CAN HEAR!!! YAY!!! :D First day of full hearing in over a week! Me so happy! ... Though I think the only CotU people who would possibly still read this LJ entry already saw my exultation in my tweet earlier today... Oh wells. I'm known for repeating my stories anyway since I talk too much and never remember who I tell my stories to in the first place. Nothing new. XD

News point 2:
Had a telephone interiew with a MD this evening.  Unfortunately, the number the MD provided me with was a wrong number. So, I called this dude twice asking for the MD.  Second time, he sounded mighty disgruntled with me.  Sad tiems.  But, it freed up my evening, so good times for me. :)

I think I'm going a little bit nuts with the impending graduation of Aichan from Morning Musume... This evening while driving home, I was accelerating (Joh was in the car with me) and had to shift up.  I had been blabbing on (as I tend to do) and forgot which gear I was in. So I interrupted myself and said "Where am I going?" (as in what gear do I need to shift to). So i looked at my speedometer and then my gearbox to figure it out (I was almost 80km/hr, so I had to go to 5th), and responded to myself "5th gen!" While Joh looked over at me and said ".... You're nuts." lolol

The other day, Love Namida Iro played on my Ipod in the car, and (again with joh in the car) I yelled out "Aichan!" *pause....* *Joh looks at me* "..... AYAYA. I MEANT AYAYA!!!"  I see many an issues with me in the coming months.

Anyway... that's all for now. My new years resolution: update LJ at least once a month ... hurpdurp. We'll see how that goes.

Also... i feel like I need an Aichan LJ icon now. XD
